  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Business Empire – Strategic Trade and Investment Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Business Empire is a multiplayer board game where players build a business empire by strategically acquiring and developing properties. Up to 6 players can join this dynamic game, purchasing properties, upgrading them, and aiming to buy out their opponents to take control. The ultimate goal is to acquire all rival properties and win the game.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free Property Selection</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/133e7d63035fc9e94ae7f7ff643d5750.poster.avif?t=1748982716\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/133e7d63035fc9e94ae7f7ff643d5750.webm?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/133e7d63035fc9e94ae7f7ff643d5750.mp4?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike traditional dice-based mechanics, players can freely choose properties based on their strategy.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Development System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/3311ff8fc0f49117769105ed1ae2ff71.poster.avif?t=1748982716\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/3311ff8fc0f49117769105ed1ae2ff71.webm?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/3311ff8fc0f49117769105ed1ae2ff71.mp4?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchased properties can be upgraded to increase their value and generate higher profits.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random Chance Cards</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/ff4a35a9114ebd978ece33d4dc96c535.poster.avif?t=1748982716\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/ff4a35a9114ebd978ece33d4dc96c535.webm?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/ff4a35a9114ebd978ece33d4dc96c535.mp4?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At certain turns, random chance cards appear, providing players with advantages or unexpected disadvantages.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Competitive Multiplayer Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/a6285a8ce7c7ca283112bd5bfb057959.poster.avif?t=1748982716\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/a6285a8ce7c7ca283112bd5bfb057959.webm?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/a6285a8ce7c7ca283112bd5bfb057959.mp4?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players compete against each other in a strategic decision-making process.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Business Empire is inspired by classic board games but offers a modern business simulation experience with greater strategic freedom. Are you ready to build your empire and outsmart your rivals?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Business Empire – Strategic Trade and Investment Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Business Empire is a multiplayer board game where players build a business empire by strategically acquiring and developing properties. Up to 6 players can join this dynamic game, purchasing properties, upgrading them, and aiming to buy out their opponents to take control. The ultimate goal is to acquire all rival properties and win the game.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free Property Selection</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/133e7d63035fc9e94ae7f7ff643d5750.poster.avif?t=1748982716\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/133e7d63035fc9e94ae7f7ff643d5750.webm?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/133e7d63035fc9e94ae7f7ff643d5750.mp4?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike traditional dice-based mechanics, players can freely choose properties based on their strategy.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Development System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/3311ff8fc0f49117769105ed1ae2ff71.poster.avif?t=1748982716\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/3311ff8fc0f49117769105ed1ae2ff71.webm?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/3311ff8fc0f49117769105ed1ae2ff71.mp4?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchased properties can be upgraded to increase their value and generate higher profits.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random Chance Cards</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/ff4a35a9114ebd978ece33d4dc96c535.poster.avif?t=1748982716\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/ff4a35a9114ebd978ece33d4dc96c535.webm?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/ff4a35a9114ebd978ece33d4dc96c535.mp4?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At certain turns, random chance cards appear, providing players with advantages or unexpected disadvantages.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Competitive Multiplayer Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/a6285a8ce7c7ca283112bd5bfb057959.poster.avif?t=1748982716\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/a6285a8ce7c7ca283112bd5bfb057959.webm?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3595430/extras/a6285a8ce7c7ca283112bd5bfb057959.mp4?t=1748982716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players compete against each other in a strategic decision-making process.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Business Empire is inspired by classic board games but offers a modern business simulation experience with greater strategic freedom. Are you ready to build your empire and outsmart your rivals?</p>",
